De quien era ella.

903
01:17:03,800 --> 01:17:05,300
Te amo.

904
01:17:05,383 --> 01:17:07,717
<i>Seguía esperando
que fuera distinto.</i>

905
01:17:07,800 --> 01:17:13,425
